aceName ref="#pmb772">Marienbad</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1899-07-15_02">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 15. 7. [1899]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1899-07-20_02">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 20. 7. [1899]</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
